000000C6                           114  GRDRUPD
000000C6                           115  ; UPDATES THE GRID ACCORDING TO 2-PLAYER GAME OF LIFE RULES AS FOLLOWS:
000000C6                           116  ; * ADDS 1 TO THE NUMBER OF GENERATIONS (GRDNGEN)
000000C6                           117  ; * SWITCHES THE MATRIX POINTERS (GRDDST AND GRDSRC).
000000C6                           118  ; * CHECKS THE NEIGHBORS USING THE NEW SOURCE MATRIX (POINTER BY GRDDRC)
000000C6                           119  ; * THE RESULTS OF APPLYING THE RULES ARE WRITTEN INTO THE NEW DESTINATION
000000C6                           120  ;   MATRIX (POINTED BY GRDDST).
000000C6                           121  ; * THE RULES ARE THE FOLLOWING, WHERE P1 AND P2 ARE 1 AND 2 RESPECTIVELY,
000000C6                           122  ;   DEAD CELLS ARE REPRESENTED BY 0 AND NP1 AND NP2 DENOTE THE NUMBER OF
000000C6                           123  ;   PLAYER 1 AND PLAYER 2 NEIGHBORS RESPECTIVELY:
000000C6                           124  ;   + SURVIVAL RULES
000000C6                           125  ;     - IF CELL IS P1 AND NP1-NP2 IS 2 OR 3 -> NEW VALUE IS P1
000000C6                           126  ;     - IF CELL IS P1 AND NP1-NP2 IS 1 AND NP1>=2 -> NEW VALUE IS P1
000000C6                           127  ;     - OTHERWISE -> NEW VALUE IS 0
000000C6                           128  ;     - IF CELL IS P2 AND NP2-NP1 IS 2 OR 3 -> NEW VALUE IS P2
000000C6                           129  ;     - IF CELL IS P2 AND NP2-NP1 IS 1 AND NP2>=2 -> NEW VALUE IS P2
000000C6                           130  ;     - OTHERWISE -> NEW VALUE IS 0
000000C6                           131  ;   + BIRTH RULES
000000C6                           132  ;     - THE CELL HAS EXACTLY THREE P1 NEIGHBOURS AND THE NUMBER
000000C6                           133  ;       OF P2 NEIGHBOURS IS DIFFERENT FROM THREE. IN THIS CASE A
000000C6                           134  ;       P1 TOKEN IS BORN IN THE CELL.
000000C6                           135  ;     - THE CELL HAS EXACTLY THREE P2 NEIGHBOURS AND THE NUMBER
000000C6                           136  ;       OF P1 NEIGHBOURS IS DIFFERENT FROM THREE. IN THIS CASE A
000000C6                           137  ;       P2 TOKEN IS BORN IN THE CELL.
000000C6                           138  ;     - THE CELL HAS EXACTLY THREE WHITE AND THREE BLACK NEIGHBOURS.
000000C6                           139  ;       IN THIS CASE AN UNBIASED COIN DETERMINES WHETHER A WHITE OR
000000C6                           140  ;       BLACK TOKEN IS BORN IN THE CELL.
000000C6                           141  ; INPUT    : NONE
000000C6                           142  ; OUTPUT   : NONE
000000C6                           143  ; MODIFIES : NONE
000000C6                           144  ; -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
000000C6                           145  
000000C6                           146  ; TODO : PLACE YOUR CODE HERE
